div.div:
(1) - Schema for storing sandbox data
Given the id of an user, the sandbox data will be stored as a hash.
The schema is defined as follows:
"user:{user_id}": {
"cNodePoolId": "1",
"cNodeId": "123",
"host": "127.0.0.1",
"port": "9100"
"protocol: "HTTP"
}
